item.title: Dr.Rhonda McEwen
item.description: Who is she? Dr.Rhonda McEwen is the current President of Victoria College at [[University of Toronto|University of Toronto St. George]] and the former Dean of [[University of Toronto|University of Toronto Mississauga]].
